<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="42" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,660,792]" pageId="5" pageNumber="42">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,660,685]" pageId="5" pageNumber="42">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Frontal triangle with margins clearly sigmoid, reaching anterior margin of frons; one row of interfrontals inside frontal triangle; frons brown; gena about 
<number box="[740,750,696,720]" pageId="5" pageNumber="42" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number box="[760,776,696,720]" pageId="5" pageNumber="42" value="4.0">4</number>
eye height, postgena about half eye height; katepisternum and metepimeron blackish on ventral half; femora blackish, hind tibia dark.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
